├── static/
│   ├── style.css
│   └── chart.png
```

---

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Install dependencies:

```
pip install flask pandas scikit-learn matplotlib
```

2. Run the application:

```
python app.py
```

3. Open in browser:

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

